&lt;p&gt;You will own a portfolio of five to eight of Mentimeter&#39;s most strategically important global customers. Your job is to ensure that what happens in Stockholm, Toronto, Sydney, and Berlin adds up to something greater than the sum of its parts and that our customers feel it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work alongside (not above) regional Strategic Account Managers and Customer Success Managers. Your influence is earned through credibility, preparation, and business understanding - not hierarchy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your initial accounts will be drawn from the management consulting sector - the professional services firms and advisory organisations that rely on Mentimeter to engage, align, and communicate across their global practices. Financial services and pharma follow as the portfolio grows.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you have existing relationships, deep familiarity, or a strong track record in any of these verticals, that matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
