&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain multi-year account plans that connect Mentimeter&#39;s value to each customer&#39;s business priorities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain C-suite and senior executive relationships across regions, functions, and buying groups&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead Executive Business Reviews that move conversations from product usage to business transformation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate regional Strategic Account Managers and Customer Success Managers around shared priorities - creating alignment without managing them&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify expansion opportunities and guide their commercial development across complex, multi-region deals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define the frameworks, playbooks, and best practices that will shape how Mentimeter manages global accounts long-term&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a strategic thought partner to the VP Strategic Accounts on portfolio direction, account prioritisation, and future growth&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
