&lt;li&gt;Design and instrument experiments using our stack: Confidence for assignment and data quality and HEX for digging into data questions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build tracking and instrumentation with discipline, so every experiment produces results we can actually trust&lt;/li&gt;
