&lt;li&gt;Raise the bar on experimentation craft within the team: strengthen how we design, instrument, and analyse experiments, and lead technical discussions that bring clarity to fuzzy problems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with the PM and Product Designer on framing and prioritising bets, and step in to drive the thinking when needed&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
