&lt;p&gt;At Mentimeter, organic growth is a core part of how we scale across both self-serve and enterprise.&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;With search evolving quickly, there’s an opportunity to rethink how we show up across queries, use cases, and increasingly AI-driven experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
